%% Diagram: Outbound message lifecycle state machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Queued: enqueue (after 202)
    Queued --> Sending: worker picks up
    Sending --> Delivered: 2xx from MX
    Sending --> Deferred: 4xx (timeout, throttle)
    Sending --> Bounced: 5xx (mailbox unknown, policy)
    Deferred --> Sending: backoff elapsed
    Deferred --> Bounced: give-up timer hit ~5d RFC 5321
    Deferred --> DelayedDSN: >4h still deferred
    DelayedDSN --> Sending: continue retrying
    Bounced --> Suppressed: hard bounce -> add to suppression list
    Delivered --> [*]
    Suppressed --> [*]
